description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Orange County, which featured the remainder of the Beverly Hills trip, Sh*ne continuing to show his awfulness, an appearance from Braunwyn's mom in an outfit that can only be described as "what the f*ck," and lots more!! Danny also reveals a family cooking show that should be in the works at a major network.
